HEMISPHERE.html - draw this

Experiment with the last 3 arguments of the context.arc() function. Standard form is:

context.arc(x, y, rad, 0, 2*Math.PI, true)

Argument 1 = x position

Argument 2 = y position

Argument 3 = radius

Argument 4 = starting angle of circle

Argument 5 = ending angle of circle

Argument 6 = fill side (which side of circle is colored)

Remember that 0 to 360 degress
